The paper deals with machine learning-based solutions for automatic image annotation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of crowdsourcing for data annotation and quality control involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with merging multiple annotations of one image. Finally, the use of a regressor for quality estimation involves machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
